As an expert in Search Engine Optimization and web development, I have focused my expertise toward marketing websites for best results.

Automation and software testing is my latest specialty, manipulating data to help speed up web design, marketing and report creation from databases or with Excel. From Winautomation to Automate and iMacros, I can provide tools bots and scripts to help streamline and speed up the processes you need for businesses. My skills and experience are varied, but my focus is speed and marketing, as well as cost reduction and web design and SEO.
I am happy to provide examples of what I can do in terms of sample proposals.
